      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 18:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Jane Street 称前交易员在加入 Millennium 之前曾嘲笑过该公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jane-street-says-ex-trader-mocked-dumb-millennium-strategies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[简街集团 (Jane Street Group) 称，一名前交易员曾嘲笑其新雇主的策略“愚蠢”，该交易员声称此人为千禧年管理公司 (Millennium Management) 窃取了价值数十亿美元的印度期权秘密策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/jane-street-says-ex-trader-mocked-dumb-millennium-strategies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 18:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥计划在预算之争中再融资 8.06 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/chicago-plans-806-million-bond-refinancing-amid-budget-standoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊 (Brandon Johnson) 正努力在年底前弥补近 10 亿美元的预算缺口，作为再融资的一部分，芝加哥计划本周发售约 8.06 亿美元的市政债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/chicago-plans-806-million-bond-refinancing-amid-budget-standoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 17:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油价格持稳，因 OPEC 不确定性抵消中国经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-2</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强，且市场担心 OPEC+ 不会推迟增产，油价企稳，削弱了中国经济逐步复苏的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-01/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-dec-2</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Dec 2024 23:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
